Special thanks to Bandai Namco and Supermassive Games for providing us with the game!

From the makers of a GTLive classic, Until Dawn, comes The Dark Pictures: Man of Medan! This game looks super creepy! I am excited to dive in and see if we can find all the totems... or, you know, regular secrets.
